OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy rain at first. Otherwise
OL,6,Fit will be mainly dry and rather
OL,7,Fcloudy, but some hazy bright or
OL,8,Foccasionally sunny spells developing
OL,9,Fin the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIncreasingly cloudy this
OL,12,Fevening with the chance of a few spots
OL,13,Fof light rain. Later in the night,
OL,14,Fclearer spells and isolated showers
OL,15,Fdevelop, accompanied by freshening
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
